com.Grateds.game.AI.lib

Interface State


  • public interface State
    Title: State

    Description: Interface which defines the basic requirements on states, needed when characterising problems as search problems. State definitions for particular search problems should extend this class, so the general search strategies can be used.

    Copyright: Copyright (c) Grateds 2014 Company: Grateds

    Version:
    0.1
    Author:
    Grateds

      • equals

        boolean equals(State other)
        Checks whether 'this' is equal to another state. This must be implemented by every concrete class implementing State.
        Parameters:
        other - is the state to compare 'this' to.
        Returns:
        true iff 'this' is equal, as a state, to 'other'.
